		description: ["Arcane Gold is Forbidden Arcanus's primary alloy — gold smelted with Arcane Crystal dust in a furnace. It's used in most of the mod's tools, armor, and magical blocks.", "It looks like gold, it works like something better. Don't waste it on decorative blocks."]
