		title: "Stellarite"
		icon: {id: "forbidden_arcanus:stellarite_piece", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Stellarite doesn't mine from ore — it arrives. A stellar event will occasionally rain star fragments into the world at night. Walk toward the light, dig where it lands. The fragment is there.", "Stellarite Pieces are used in Forbidden Arcanus's highest-tier gear and the Eternal Stella, which is the mod's ultimate material. Don't let the pieces sit in a chest."]
