		title: "The Everdawn"
		icon: {id: "blue_skies:everdawn_portal_frame", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Blue Skies adds two alternate dimensions accessed through dedicated portals. The Everdawn is the day-side — eternal golden light, unique biomes, mobs, and resources that don't exist in the overworld.", "Build the Everdawn portal frame and light it. Go through. Bring a waystone or mark your portal coordinates — the dimension generates fresh chunks with no regard for where you entered."]
